WEBVTT

00:00:02.354 --> 00:00:09.731 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There was a reason why 
God brought the truth to you

00:00:10.065 --> 00:00:15.941 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And called you 
from the darkness to the light.

00:00:15.941 --> 00:00:23.902 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Within your heart, 
he saw the longing that you had

00:00:23.902 --> 00:00:30.654 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To search for him 
and practice what is right.

00:00:30.654 --> 00:00:36.405 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You promised him in prayer 
to do his will;

00:00:36.947 --> 00:00:43.449 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He helped you then, 
and he will help you still.

00:00:44.324 --> 00:00:51.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jesus’ blood He bought you, 
to God you now belong.

00:00:51.201 --> 00:00:57.994 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So he will make you firm, 
and he will make you strong.

00:00:57.994 --> 00:01:04.871 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He’ll guide you and protect you, 
as he has all along.

00:01:04.871 --> 00:01:15.832 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, he will make you firm, 
and he will make you strong.

00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:25.710 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God gave his own beloved Son 
in your behalf;

00:01:25.710 --> 00:01:31.670 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
On this account, 
He wants you to succeed.

00:01:31.670 --> 00:01:39.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If He did not withhold 
the gift of His dear Son,

00:01:39.255 --> 00:01:45.174 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then never doubt He’ll give 
the strength you need.

00:01:46.007 --> 00:01:51.467 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He won’t forget the faith 
and love you’ve shown;

00:01:52.801 --> 00:01:59.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He will not fail 
to care for all His own.

00:01:59.802 --> 00:02:06.304 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With Jesus’ blood He bought you, 
to God you now belong.

00:02:06.304 --> 00:02:12.889 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So he will make you firm, 
and he will make you strong.

00:02:12.889 --> 00:02:20.433 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He’ll guide you and protect you, 
as he has all along.

00:02:20.433 --> 00:02:31.103 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Yes, he will make you firm, 
and he will make you strong.

